 Session - 23

# Shopping Cart Task

### How to run/use the application:

1. Click on the "Add to cart" button to add the product to your cart.
2. You can add as many products as you wish in the cart.
3. You can see the total number of products added to the cart at the top.
4. If you don't want the product anymore, click the "Remove from cart" button to remove the product from the cart.
5. Only the products you have added will be in your cart and not the removed ones.


